STATUS_FORMAT1 and STATUS_FORMAT2 define how the 2 status bars will appear.
By default only one of the status bars is displayed. /window double on will
make a double status bar, and /window split on will make a status bar on top
and one on the bottom of the screen. Any color changes you want must be set
in the STATUS_FORMAT* as well as the various STATUS_ variables. The
status_user* variables are for scripters to define things they would like to
appear in the topic bar.



